    <body>
        <p>In addition to replacing images in topics, you can also replace images used in skins. You can replace logos in Flare's HTML5 skins, and you can replace the About box in Mobile and WebHelp skins. </p>
        <p>To replace the skin image, open the skin in the Translation Editor, then click <img src="../../../../Images/replace_skin_images_btn.png" alt="" title="" class="ReduceButtonSize" /> in the local toolbar. The Replace Skin Images dialog opens. You can see a preview of the current skin image in the dialog. Click <span class="Emphasis">Browse</span>  to select a new image. </p>
    </body>
